		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Welcome to NesDev! <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />  Always exciting when someone has homebrew to share in their first post!<br /><br />Sort of reminds me of knytt stories - which is a good thing, of course! <br /><br />Some constructive criticism:<br />-If i'd add or change <em>one</em> more thing, it'd be an animation for climbing. It'd help informing the players what they can and cannot do. <br /><br />-If i'd change a second thing, it'd be to give the vines a bit of a &quot;drop shadow&quot; to distinguish them from the background: green on red can be hard on the eye, and some might not be able to tell the difference (colour blindness).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
