	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Palettes, huh?<br /><br />Experiment with them in your emulator's palette editor/Hex editor and then tell me the palette I should use, along with some screenshots.<br /><br />The palettes are:<br />Intro: day sky + palettes for friend/shadow figure sprites<br />Day/Red/Sunset/Night: the respective sky + palettes for enemy/rope sprites<br />Finale: night sky + palettes for friend/shadow figure sprites<br />Every palette contains ground colors.<br /><br />For more advanced graphics changes, fork the game on GitHub. The link to the repo is on the Itch.io page.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


